title: DEQ announces its 2015 Third Quarter Results Release Date and Conference Call
text:
DEQ SYSTEMS CORP.
LAS VEGAS, NV and LÃ‰VIS, QC, Oct. 21, 2015 /PRNewswire/ - DEQ Systems Corp. (TSXV: DEQ) ("DEQ" or the "Company") announced today that the Company plans to release its financial results for the third quarter ended August 31, 2015 on Wednesday, October 28, 2015 after the closing of the Canadian markets. The Consolidated Financial Statements will be available on SEDAR ( www.sedar.com ) and on DEQ's website ( www.deq.com ).
A conference call will be held on Thursday, October 29, 2015 at 4:30pm EDT to present and discuss these results. Those interested in participating should dial toll free 1 (877) 223-4471 or (647) 788-4922.
Please note that the conference call replay will be available until November 11, 2015 by dialing (416) 621-4642 or 1 (800) 585-8367. The passcode for the replay is 60956941.
